-- German Government to Tackle Fuel-Price Fluctuations, Bild Says
-- B y   J a n a   R a n d o w
-- 2012-03-28T05:51:49Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-28/german-government-to-tackle-fuel-price-fluctuations-bild-says.html
The German government’s coalition
parties are planning to work out a concept to prevent excessive
price fluctuations at the gas pump,  Bild  newspaper reported,
citing unidentified lawmakers.  First proposals will be made before the Easter holidays,
Bild said.  Germany ’s cartel office and the economy ministry will
contribute to drafting a response to price changes of as much as
15 euro cents ($0.2) a day recently, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jana Randow in Frankfurt at 
 jrandow@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
